{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/privacy/layout,_N_T_/privacy/page,_N_T_/privacy"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/5311a7fc74388d15.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-616e068a201ad621.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/fd9d1056-b11b2651f33aae7f.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/117-4f5b424f20efdcae.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-0bca0c59044d953b.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/privacy/page-0930084df9b46e35.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-afc0aad3ee7a9a8e.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://api.fontshare.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#050505\"/><title>Privacy Policy | Enerium</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Read how Enerium collects, protects, stores, and processes health, nutrition, fitness, and analytics data across the app and website.\"/><meta name=\"application-name\" content=\"Enerium\"/><link rel=\"author\" href=\"https://enerium.app\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"Enerium\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.webmanifest\" crossorigin=\"use-credentials\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Enerium privacy policy,health app privacy,nutrition app privacy,fitness data policy\"/><meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"origin-when-cross-origin\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"Enerium\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"Enerium\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><meta name=\"category\" content=\"Health &amp; Fitness\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://enerium.app/privacy\"/><meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no, address=no, email=no\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-title\" content=\"Enerium\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"black-translucent\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Privacy Policy | Enerium\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Read how Enerium collects, protects, stores, and processes health, nutrition, fitness, and analytics data across the app and website.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://enerium.app/privacy\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Enerium\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://enerium.app/opengraph-image\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Your Health, Reimagined by AI\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Privacy Policy | Enerium\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Read how Enerium collects, protects, stores, and processes health, nutrition, fitness, and analytics data across the app and website.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://enerium.app/twitter-image\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-icon\"/><script defer=\"\" data-domain=\"enerium.app\" src=\"https://plausible.io/js/script.js\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-void font-inter text-white\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Enerium\",\"url\":\"https://enerium.app\",\"logo\":\"https://enerium.app/logo.png\",\"description\":\"AI-powered health app for nutrition tracking, meal planning, hydration reminders, fitness syncing, and wellness analytics in one platform.\",\"email\":\"hello@enerium.app\",\"contactPoint\":[{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"customer support\",\"email\":\"hello@enerium.app\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"en\"]},{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"privacy support\",\"email\":\"privacy@enerium.app\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"en\"]},{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"legal support\",\"email\":\"legal@enerium.app\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"en\"]}]},{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Enerium\",\"url\":\"https://enerium.app\",\"description\":\"AI-powered health app for nutrition tracking, meal planning, hydration reminders, fitness syncing, and wellness analytics in one platform.\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"MobileApplication\",\"name\":\"Enerium\",\"url\":\"https://enerium.app\",\"applicationCategory\":\"HealthApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"iOS, Android\",\"description\":\"AI-powered health app for nutrition tracking, meal planning, hydration reminders, fitness syncing, and wellness analytics in one platform.\",\"featureList\":[\"Nutrition Intelligence\",\"Fitness & Activity\",\"Smart Hydration\",\"AI Kitchen\",\"Deep Analytics\"]}]}</script><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ambient-bg pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ambient-bg__base\"></div><div class=\"ambient-bg__aurora ambient-bg__aurora--1\"></div><div class=\"ambient-bg__aurora ambient-bg__aurora--2\"></div><div class=\"ambient-bg__aurora ambient-bg__aurora--3\"></div><div class=\"ambient-bg__noise\"></div><div class=\"ambient-bg__vignette\"></div></div><canvas aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 z-[1] mix-blend-screen\"></canvas><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#050505] text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"relative z-10 mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/40 transition-colors hover:text-white\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">←</span><span>Back to Home</span></a><h1 class=\"font-satoshi text-4xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-white/30\">Last updated: April 2026</p><div class=\"mt-12 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60\"><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">1. Information We Collect</h2><p>We collect information you provide directly: account details (email, name), health data (nutrition logs, fitness activity, body metrics), and usage data. We also collect device information and analytics to improve the service.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">2. How We Use Your Data</h2><p>Your data is used to provide personalized health recommendations, power AI features (Vision AI, meal planning, adaptive intelligence), sync with health platforms (Apple Health, Google Fit), and improve our service quality.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">3. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2><p>All health data is encrypted end-to-end using industry-standard AES-256 encryption. Data is stored on secure servers with strict access controls. We conduct regular security audits and penetration testing.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">4. Data Sharing</h2><p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal health data to third parties. Data may be shared only with your explicit consent, or when required by law. Third-party integrations (Apple Health, Google Fit) operate under their respective privacy policies.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">5. AI &amp; Machine Learning</h2><p>Our AI models process your data on-device when possible. When cloud processing is needed, data is anonymized and encrypted in transit. AI models are not trained on individual user data without explicit opt-in consent.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">6. Your Rights</h2><p>You have the right to: access your data, correct inaccurate data, delete your account and all associated data, export your data in standard formats, and opt out of non-essential data processing. Contact us to exercise any of these rights.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">7. Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2><p>Our website uses essential cookies for functionality. We use privacy-respecting analytics to understand usage patterns. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-3 font-satoshi text-lg font-bold text-white\">8. Contact</h2><p>For privacy-related questions or data requests, contact our Data Protection team at <span class=\"text-[#B7F46B]\">privacy@enerium.app</span></p></section></div></div></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-616e068a201ad621.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/5311a7fc74388d15.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2:I[2846,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[2168,[\\\"385\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/privacy/page-0930084df9b46e35.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[4707,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[6423,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n8:I[1785,[\\\"185\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-afc0aad3ee7a9a8e.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\na:I[1060,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:T5a1,{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@graph\\\":[{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Enerium\\\",